            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "رَجُلٍ أَعْطَى عَبْدَهُ عَشَرَةَ دَرَاهِمَ عَلَى أَنْ يُؤَدِّيَ اَلْعَبْدُ كُلَّ شَهْرٍ عَشَرَةَ دَرَاهِمَ أَ يَحِلُّ ذَلِكَ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " قَالَ"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:2:5:26",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/27/26",
      "text": [
        " \"لاَ بَأْسَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4016 - Ali ibn Ja'far asked his brother Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as) about a man who gave his servant ten dirhams on the condition that the servant would pay back ten dirhams each month.\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm in that.\""
        ]
      }
    },
